title: Midnight Serenade
description: A moody exploration of city lights reflecting on rain-slicked streets, capturing the solitude of the urban night. Thick impasto oil strokes contrast with delicate glazes.

title: Ephemeral Bloom
description: An abstract interpretation of spring flora in decay. The vibrant pinks and reds are violently interrupted by charcoal greys, symbolizing the fleeting nature of beauty.

title: Study of Silence
description: A hyper-realistic graphite study of a lone figure. The heavy shading creates a sculpture-like depth on the flat paper, representing the stoic witness of history.

title: Digital Horizon V
description: Acrylic on canvas. A manual reproduction of digital glitches, exploring the intersection of algorithmic chaos and human-curated color palettes.

title: Crimson Tide
description: A large-scale seascape that borders on abstraction. The overwhelming power of the ocean is depicted through aggressive knife work and a monochromatic red palette.

title: Fractured Memory
description: Graphite and charcoal on textured paper. A commentary on how memory degrades, featuring erased sections and rewritten lines.

title: Golden Solstice
description: Warm, radiating gold leaf applied over a textured dark acrylic background. The piece changes character dramatically depending on the angle of light.

title: Urban Decay Sketch
description: Detailed pencil work featuring rust, concrete, and steel. A brutalist appreciation of industrial structures reclaiming their space in nature.
